# Crash Recovery Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant App
    participant SessionStore
    participant RecoveryStore
    participant BookmarkManager
    participant User

    App->>SessionStore: Load latest-session.json
    App->>RecoveryStore: Check dirty recovery buffers
    App->>BookmarkManager: Resolve workspace bookmark

    alt Recovery exists
        App->>User: Offer restore recovered session
        User->>App: Restore
        App->>SessionStore: Restore tabs/layout/cursors
        App->>RecoveryStore: Restore dirty buffer text
        App->>User: Show restored dirty tabs
    else No recovery
        App->>User: Open normal workspace/welcome
    end
```
